    participant FE as 前端页面
    participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen
    participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV
    participant ProdSV as UnifyProductCentre服务
    participant ElecSV as IElecSV
    participant NumSV as INumberIntfQuerySV
    participant DB as 数据库
    participant HW as 读卡器硬件

    Note over User,DB: 主流程：携号转网用户开户

    User->>FE: 输入携入号码
    FE->>Page: checkAccessNum ACCESS_NUM NP_BACK
    Page->>OpenSV: checkAccessNum
    OpenSV->>DB: SELECT 携转用户表 号码资源表
