<h3 id="33-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%89%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E5%92%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9">3.3 子流程三：套餐和活动选择</h3>
