<h3 id="35-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%BA%94%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B">3.5 子流程五：提交开户（核心流程）</h3>
<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 提交完整的携转开户业务数据，创建用户、账户、套餐订购、携转关系等记录。</p>
<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-mermaid"><div class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 工作人员
    participant FE as 前端
    participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen
    participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV
    participant CustSV as ICCOutOperateSV
    participant DB as 数据库

    User->>FE: 点击 提交
    FE->>FE: submitBeforeCheck 全面校验
    FE->>FE: checkHasActive 校验套餐关联活动
    FE->>FE: $.cssubmit.submitTrade 组装提交数据
    FE->>Page: onTradeSubmit 全部表单数据
    activate Page

