    else 开户成功
        Page->>CustSV: addOperLog 记录操作日志
        activate CustSV
        CustSV->>DB: INSERT 操作日志表
        CustSV-->>Page: 成功
        deactivate CustSV
        Page-->>FE: 开户成功
    end
    deactivate Page
</div></code></pre>
<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>前端：<code>submitBeforeCheck()</code> -&gt; 全面校验 -&gt; <code>checkHasActive</code> -&gt; <code>$.cssubmit.submitTrade()</code> -&gt; <code>onTradeSubmit</code></li>
<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.onTradeSubmit(IRequestCycle)</code></li>
