<h3 id="36-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%AD%E5%80%BC%E7%8F%AD%E9%95%BF%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83">3.6 子流程六：值班长验证码授权</h3>
<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 对于吉祥号码等特殊场景，需要值班长工号发送验证码并校验通过后才能继续办理。</p>
<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-mermaid"><div class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 工作人员
    participant FE as 前端
    participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen
    participant OpenSV as ISubscriberOpenSV
    participant DB as 验证码表

    Note over User,DB: 发送验证码

    User->>FE: 输入值班长工号 点击发送验证码
    FE->>FE: sendYzm 校验工号格式(8位)
    FE->>Page: dealYzm MANAGER_STAFF ACCESS_NUM ACTION=SEND_YZM
    activate Page
    Page->>OpenSV: dealYzm
    activate OpenSV
    OpenSV->>DB: 生成验证码 发送短信
    DB-->>OpenSV: 成功
    OpenSV-->>Page: returnValue returnMsg
    deactivate OpenSV
    Page-->>FE: 发送结果
    deactivate Page
    FE-->>User: 提示发送成功

