<h3 id="37-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%83%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C">3.7 子流程七：智能助手校验</h3>
