<h3 id="38-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%AB%E5%90%89%E7%A5%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C">3.8 子流程八：吉祥号码权限校验</h3>
<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 对于吉祥号码开户，需要通过值班长验证码授权才能继续办理。</p>
<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-mermaid"><div class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as 前端
    participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen
    participant NumSV as INumberIntfQuerySV
    participant PrivSV as ISecPrivOperSV
    participant DB as 数据库

    FE->>Page: initIMPOWER ACCESS_NUM IS_CHKRULE
    activate Page
    Page->>NumSV: querySingNumInfo ACCESS_NUM
    activate NumSV
    NumSV->>DB: SELECT 号码信息 判断是否吉祥号
    DB-->>NumSV: ISLUCKY
    deactivate NumSV

    alt ISLUCKY == 1 吉祥号码
        Page->>PrivSV: insertLuckyNumBusiLog 记录吉祥号操作日志
        activate PrivSV
        PrivSV->>DB: INSERT 吉祥号操作日志表
        PrivSV-->>Page: 成功
        deactivate PrivSV
        Page-->>FE: ISLUCKY=1
        FE->>FE: 显示验证码授权区域 IMPOWER
    else 非吉祥号码
        Page-->>FE: ISLUCKY!=1
        FE->>FE: 隐藏验证码授权区域
    end
    deactivate Page
</div></code></pre>
<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>前端：<code>$.NpSubscriberOpen.init()</code> -&gt; 获取登录号码 -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(&quot;&quot;, &quot;initIMPOWER&quot;, param, &quot;NpSubHiddenPart&quot;, ...)</code></li>
<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.initIMPOWER(IRequestCycle)</code></li>
<li>业务层：
<ol>
<li><code>this.call(&quot;ResourceCentre.resource.INumberIntfQuerySV.querySingNumInfo&quot;)</code> - 查询号码是否为吉祥号</li>
<li><code>this.call(&quot;BusiFrame.priv.ISecPrivOperSV.insertLuckyNumBusiLog&quot;)</code> - 记录吉祥号操作日志</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>数据库：号码信息表（SELECT）、吉祥号操作日志表（INSERT）</li>
</ul>
